msgstr "用于解析出站域名及以下绕过域名的 DNS"

msgid "Bypassed domain rules"
msgstr "绕过域名规则"

msgid "Specify rules like <code>geosite:cn</code> or <code>domain:bilibili.com</code>. See <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">documentation</a> for details."
msgstr "填写如 <code>geosite:cn</code> 或 <code>domain:bilibili.com</code> 之类的规则。详情见 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。"

msgid "Specify rules like <code>domain:bilibili.com</code> or see <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">documentation</a> for details.<br/> In order to use Geosite rules you need a valid resource file /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat.<br/>Compile your firmware again with data files to use Geosite rules, or <a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">download one</a> and upload it to your router."
msgstr "填写如 <code>domain:bilibili.com</code> 之类的规则，或查看 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。<br/>若要使用 Geosite 规则，需要有效的资源文件 /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat。<br/>你可以重新编译带数据文件的固件，或者<a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">下载一个</a>后上传到路由器。"

msgid "Secure DNS"
msgstr "安全 DNS"

msgid "DNS for resolving known polluted domains (specify forwarded domain rules here)"
msgstr "用于解析已知污染域名的 DNS（在这里填写转发域名规则）"

msgid "Forwarded domain rules"
msgstr "转发域名规则"

msgid "Specify rules like <code>geosite:geolocation-!cn</code> or <code>domain:youtube.com</code>. See <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">documentation</a> for details."
msgstr "填写如 <code>geosite:geolocation-!cn</code> 或 <code>domain:youtube.com</code> 之类的规则。详情见 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。"

msgid "Specify rules like <code>domain:youtube.com</code> or see <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">documentation</a> for details.<br/> In order to use Geosite rules you need a valid resource file /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat.<br/>Compile your firmware again with data files to use Geosite rules, or <a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">download one</a> and upload it to your router."
msgstr "填写如 <code>domain:youtube.com</code> 之类的规则，或查看 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。<br/>若要使用 Geosite 规则，需要有效的资源文件 /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat。<br/>你可以重新编译带数据文件的固件，或者<a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">下载一个</a>后上传到路由器。"

msgid "Default DNS"
msgstr "默认 DNS"

msgid "DNS for resolving other sites (not in the rules above) and DNS records other than A or AAAA (TXT and MX for example)"
msgstr "用于解析其它站点（不在上方规则中）以及非 A / AAAA 记录（如 TXT、MX）的 DNS"

msgid "Blocked domain rules"
msgstr "阻止域名规则"

