msgstr "填写如 <code>geosite:category-ads</code> 或 <code>domain:baidu.com</code> 之类的规则。详情见 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。"

msgid "Specify rules like <code>domain:baidu.com</code> or see <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">documentation</a> for details.<br/> In order to use Geosite rules you need a valid resource file /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat.<br/>Compile your firmware again with data files to use Geosite rules, or <a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">download one</a> and upload it to your router."
msgstr "填写如 <code>domain:baidu.com</code> 之类的规则，或查看 <a href=\"https://xtls.github.io/config/dns.html#dnsobject\">文档</a>。<br/>若要使用 Geosite 规则，需要有效的资源文件 /usr/share/xray/geosite.dat。<br/>你可以重新编译带数据文件的固件，或者<a href=\"https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community\">下载一个</a>后上传到路由器。"

msgid "Blocked to loopback"
msgstr "阻止到回环地址"

msgid "Return <code>127.127.127.127</code> as response for blocked domain rules. If not selected, <code>NXDOMAIN</code> will be returned."
msgstr "对被阻止的域名规则返回 <code>127.127.127.127</code>。若不选择，则返回 <code>NXDOMAIN</code>。"

msgid "Xray DNS Server Port"
msgstr "Xray DNS 服务器端口"

msgid "Do not use port 53 (dnsmasq), port 5353 (mDNS) or other common ports"
msgstr "不要使用 53（dnsmasq）、5353（mDNS）或其它常见端口"

msgid "Extra DNS Server Ports"
msgstr "额外 DNS 服务器端口"

msgid "Listen for DNS Requests on multiple ports (all of which serves as dnsmasq upstream servers).<br/>For example if Xray DNS Server Port is 5300 and use 3 extra ports, 5300 - 5303 will be used for DNS requests.<br/>Increasing this value may help reduce the possibility of temporary DNS lookup failures."
msgstr "在多个端口监听 DNS 请求（这些端口都会作为 dnsmasq 的上游 DNS 服务器）。<br/>例如 Xray DNS 服务器端口为 5300，额外端口数为 3，则会使用 5300 - 5303 处理 DNS 请求。<br/>适当增大该值有助于减少临时 DNS 查询失败。"

msgid "Address Pool (IPv4)"
msgstr "地址池（IPv4）"

msgid "Address Pool Size (IPv4)"
msgstr "地址池大小（IPv4）"

msgid "Address Pool (IPv6)"
